{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Dm]Anthony works in the gro[Gm7]cery store
[C]Savin' his pe[Caug]nnies for someday[Fmaj7]
[Dm]Mama Leone left a [Gm7]note on the door
She said [C]"Sonny, move out[Caug]    to the coun[Fmaj7]try" 
{end_of_verse}


