{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[Dm]Sergeant O'Leary is wal[Gm7]kin' the beat
At [C]night he becomes[Caug]    a bar[Fmaj7]tender
He works at [Dm]Mister. Cacciatore's down on [Gm7]Sullivan Street
Ac[C]ross from the me[Caug]dical center[Fmaj7]
{end_of_verse}


{start_of_part: Pre-Chorus}
